snippet: Joanne Schivley said The Vallejo Times-Herald’s requirement that she present documents to back her claims in a campaign ad had “a chilling effect on the political process.”
lead_paragraph: Joanne Schivley said The Vallejo Times-Herald’s requirement that she present documents to back her claims in a campaign ad had “a chilling effect on the political process.”

headline.main: Mayoral Contender Sees Bias in a Newspaper’s Ad Rules
headline.seo: Schivley, Mayoral Candidate, Sees Bias in Vallejo Times-Herald Policy
